PS:I try The Grim and Somber ENBS-Hircine ( http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/50501/? ) with my potato so pictures little dark i guess and sorry for my bad language.

Follow these steps:

1. Download my mod and install it at data/skse/plugins/chargen/presets
2. Open Skyrim using SKSE
3. Load any working save file
4. Open the console
5. Type showracemenu
6. Select the Nord Race
7. Look for the slide option "preset slot"
8. Press F9 and done
author: RolloTheBerserker
